Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.95,0:00:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}안 좋은 예감...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.15,0:00:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}정중해버렸다...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,으응...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.71,0:00:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,니지카 녀석들이\N만들어놓고 갔거든...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.30,0:00:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,결국...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,태풍 와버렸네요
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.94,0:00:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐, 테루테루보즈로\N어떻게 될 문제가 아니니깐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,이래서는
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.37,0:00:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,티켓 사준 사람들조차\N안 오는 거 아닐까요?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,다들, 관객수 보고\N마음 꺾이지나 않으면 좋을 텐데
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,연습도 열심히 했는데\N안타깝게 됐네요
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,밴드 계속할 거라면...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.51,0:00:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,이렇게 억까 당하는 일도\N잔뜩 생길 테니까...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.87,0:00:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,어떤 상황이든\N극복할 수 있게 돼야지...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.55,0:00:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,손수건 드릴까요?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 좀 꺼져봐...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:00:56.99,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna천생연분\fs60\bord0\pos(885,915)\c&H353B23&}티켓 판매는 {\c&H204E48&}17:00부터 {\c&H313822&}시작합니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.13,0:00:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,친구들도...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.20,0:00:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,역시 못 오나봐요
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.53,0:01:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,저..저희 부모님도...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,하..할머니께서 후타리를\N봐주기로 하셨는데요
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.42,0:01:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,모..못 오게 되셔서...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.85,0:01:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,그렇구나~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.91,0:01:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,그럴 수밖에 없겠지~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.74,0:01:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,절반 이하로 줄어버렸네요\N관객수...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.52,0:01:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,어쩔 수 없지!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.74,0:01:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,마음 다잡고 가자!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.97,0:01:17.88,Default - A,,0,0,0,,네, 그래야죠!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.19,0:01:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}니지카쨩은\N어떤 때든 명랑하구나...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.32,0:01:21.48,Default - Right,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fna두리둥실\fs45\pos(1175,530)}하아아~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.28,0:01:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,얘가 진짜~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.30,0:01:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,못 말려~\N긴장감도 없네~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.88,0:01:26.25,Default - A,,0,0,0,,저기압...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.25,0:01:27.71,Default - A,,0,0,0,,졸려...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그러고 보니 도우미로\N참가했던 라이브 때도...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.11,0:01:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}무서워 하던\N나를 격려해줬던가...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.56,0:01:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}조..좋았어!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.63,0:01:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}나도!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.77,0:01:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}오늘 라이브!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.78,0:01:41.74,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fn@a두리둥실\fs35\bord5\c&H1C1B19&\3c&HF4F6F6&\frz294\pos(1013,510)\iclip(m 928 513 l 937 495 953 467 964 449 975 436 996 410 1012 395 1013 386 1014 416 1010 438 1006 451 1013 446 1025 430 1025 418 1028 410 1032 430 1035 442 1042 443 1036 452 1027 469 1013 489 1000 516 987 537 973 558 961 584 946 610 931 638 920 659 906 686 891 709 877 726 861 748 851 762 852 769 845 765 849 741 849 721 859 694 865 667 868 653 867 635 865 632)}관광친선대사
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.78,0:01:41.74,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fn@a두리둥실\fs35\bord5\c&H1C1B19&\3c&HF4F6F6&\frz242.4\pos(975,580)}일일순사부장
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\fs100}마구 달궈보자!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.47,0:01:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.26,0:01:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,오늘은 진지한 라이브니까\N장난치면 안 된다~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,그거\N마음에 들었나봐요!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.96,0:01:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 네에...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.31,0:01:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,우와~\N비 엄청 쏟아진다~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.73,0:01:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,벗쯰쨩~\N나 왔당~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.91,0:01:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 언니...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.33,0:01:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,어?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.81,0:01:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,너, 봇치쨩 보려고\N온 거냐?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.82,0:01:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,그뤃다그~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.17,0:01:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,예에이~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.85,0:02:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,어...\N아는 사이셨어요?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,나 대학 다닐 적\N후배...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.71,0:02:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,이찌, 이찌~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.99,0:02:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,오늘 라이브\N뒷풀이 할끄지~?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.49,0:02:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,술집은\N이미 알아봤어엉~?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,술냄새 쩌네...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,맛있게 잘 하는 집\N잘 알걸랑요~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.35,0:02:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,들어바, 들어바아~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.04,0:02:17.72,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,00)\fna두리둥실\fs55\pos(455,770)}오늘밤도~\N밤새 마셔버리장~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.72,0:02:19.47,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\fna두리둥실\fs55\pos(455,770)}우후후후~♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.47,0:02:20.20,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,10)\fna두리둥실\fs55\pos(455,770)}에헤헤헤헤~♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,또 한 층 더\N성가신 놈이 돼버렸구만
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,막 술자리에 재미들린\N대학생이랑 맞먹게 성가시네요~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.77,0:02:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,그보다, 너\N다 젖은 꼴로 달라붙냐!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.36,0:02:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,다 젖었네~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.80,0:02:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 히토리쨩!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}아, 저번 버스킹 때...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.12,0:02:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,저..정말\N와주신 거예요?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,물론이지!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.64,0:02:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,그야 우리는\N히토리쨩의 팬인걸!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.44,0:02:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,태풍을 날려버릴만큼\N멋진 연주, 기대할게요!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.67,0:02:51.54,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fna두리둥실\fs55\pos(1125,500)}흐…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.24,0:02:51.54,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fna두리둥실\fs55\pos(1495,545)}흐히힣…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:51.54,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fna두리둥실\fs55\pos(1225,605)}헤헿…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:51.54,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fna두리둥실\fs55\pos(1330,710)}팬…?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.47,0:02:51.54,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fna두리둥실\fs55\pos(1525,770)}아흫 으힣히
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.29,0:02:51.54,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fna두리둥실\fs55\pos(1170,820)}흐흐흫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,히..히토리쨩 맞지...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,사람을 잘못봤나...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}내 팬이래~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fna두리둥실}축하해!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.12,0:02:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fna두리둥실}축하해, 축하해!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.18,0:02:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fna두리둥실}축하해, 축하해, 축하해~!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.12,0:03:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}내 팬이래애애~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.48,0:03:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,큭, 크힣 흫흫흫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,1000)}-사람 잘못 봤어요~!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:07.96,Default - Right,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,10)\pos(1880,1040)}fan sub by kairan
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,비...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,앞으로\N점점 더 세지려나봐요
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.97,0:03:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,지금보다 더?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,네...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,이제 그냥 라이브 상황을\N스트리밍으로 띄워서
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,처음부터\N무관객 라이브였단 걸로...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.52,0:03:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,안 해, 안 해~!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,그래봐야 이제 와서\N갑자기 볼 사람도 없고
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,몇 명인가는\N이미 와주셨잖아~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960.32,981.36)}괘괘괘...!
