Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.52,0:10:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,저는 아직도 Rock에 대해서\N이해가 많이 모자란가 봐요...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.59,0:10:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,아마 이해 안 해도\N별 문제 없을 거 같은데...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,라이브~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,마지막에는 마구 달아올라서\N다행이었지~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.76,0:10:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,관객은 10명 정도밖에\N없었지만요!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,그래도~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,그 사람들은\N다들 만족해줬잖음~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.39,0:10:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,그러려나요♪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,계속하다 보면\N팬은 알아서 점점 늘어
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,다음 라이브 때도\N열심히 잘해봐라
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.88,0:11:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,목표 할당량은\N제대로 내시고
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,0:11:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,마지막 한 줄만 없었으면\N감동했을 텐데...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.62,0:11:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩도 오늘은\N엄청 열심히 잘했지~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,근데...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,어!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,새하얗게\N불태워버렸나!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩~\N재가 되진 말자~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:18.59,Default - Right,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1880,1040)\fad(500,500)\fna두리둥실\fs45\bord5\c&H935534&\3c&HFFFFFF&}※ 내일의 죠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.29,0:11:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,난 이제 지쳤어...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:22.76,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,600)\fna두리둥실\fs55\move(525,140,525,330,00,2600)}축하해, 축하해~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:22.76,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,600)\fna두리둥실\fs55\move(1425,110,1425,300,00,2600)}축하해, 축하해~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,그건 다른 작품이고!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.15,0:11:23.90,Default - Right,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1880,1040)\fad(500,500)\fna두리둥실\fs45\bord5\c&H935534&\3c&HFFFFFF&}※ 플랜더스의 개
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 뭐냐!\N먹고 싶은 요리 시켜!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.89,0:11:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,헉...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 옙...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩은\N뭐 먹을래~?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 난 말이지~\N닭튀김 시킬까 하는데~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 괘..괜찮네요...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,있잖아, 그건...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,이소스타예요!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.28,0:11:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,제가 장관이라서요!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.29,0:11:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,장관??
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,그거 말야...\N뭐가 재밌는 거냐?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,네?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,즐거운 기분을\N서로 나누는 거라고 할지...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,친구가 즐거워 보이면\N덩달아 즐겁지 않아요?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:50.60,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(940,00)\fna입술l\3c&H5E9CE8&\pos(630,210)}키~따앙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:12:02.16,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,10)\fna입술l\3c&H5E9CE8&\move(630,210,980,210,00,480)}키~따앙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:12:02.16,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(940,10)\fna입술l\b0\fs50\bord3\3c&H5E9CE8&\pos(420,790)}키따~앙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:12:02.16,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(940,10)\fna입술l\b0\fs60\bord3\3c&H5E9CE8&\pos(1420,840)}키따~앙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.95,0:11:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,윽...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.84,0:11:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,잘한다~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,키타쨩 파워로 언니의\N비뚤어진 체질을 정화해버려~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,비뚤어져요?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,점장님 원래\N다정하시잖아요~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,그만해...\N나 죽어...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.31,0:12:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,저..저기...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,저는 다 골라서\N메뉴판 보세요...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,고마워!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 보자...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼 저는
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,아보카도랑 크림치즈\N핀초로 할게요!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,윽...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1230,980)}그리고...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1230,980)}스패니쉬 오믈렛\N오랑데즈 소스 곁들임으로 할게요!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1230,980)}뭐라고...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1230,980)}이 오믈렛은 오랑데즈 소스랑\N나오는 거거든요!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1230,980)\fad(00,600)}오란다...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.33,0:12:23.95,Default - A,,0,0,0,,응~?\N좋은데, 좋은데~!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:25.61,Default - A,,0,0,0,,팍팍 시키자~!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\pos(1190,980)}키타 씨...\N또 의미불명인...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\pos(1190,980)}멋쟁이같은 단어를\N말하고 있어...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\pos(1190,980)}키타 씨는 스타퍼 같은 데도\N평범하게 들어갈 수 있겠지...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.07,0:12:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\pos(1180,980)}어..어려운 주문도\N막 자연스럽게 튀어나오고!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fna두리둥실\fs70}페페로프리프리\N파피푸페포~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.47,0:12:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fna두리둥실\fs70\fad(00,600)}페로페파치나\N쇼트로 주세요♪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,600)\fna피오피동글\b0\fs70\bord5\fscy1\t(00,100,\fscx90\fscy150)\t(100,200,\fscx120\fscy80)\t(200,300,\fscx100\fscy100)\frz20.41\pos(677,560)\c&HCFE1FB&\3c&H5252EF&}키땅{\fna두리둥실}♥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩은?\N뭐 시킬래?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.72,0:12:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,뜨헉...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\pos(1105,980)}오..오늘의 나는\N좀 다르다고!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\pos(1105,980)}나도 아무거나\N멋짐 터지는 초이스를!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 그럼...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,마..마추픽추 유적의
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,미시시피강
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,그랜드 캐니언
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,샌디에고 모듬으로~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.40,0:12:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,흠, 흠~\N마추픽추, 마추픽추...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,근데, 엉...?\N어디 있는 건데??
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:12:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 잘못 말했어요...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,감자튀김이에요...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,뭘 어떻게\N잘못 읽은 건데...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.02,0:13:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,저는 술도둑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:06.31,Default - Right,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1880,1040)\fad(500,500)\fna두리둥실\fs45\bord5\c&H2A688C&\3c&HFFFFFF&}※ 가다랑어 내장으로 담근 젓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,넌 또 몇 살이야~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.88,0:13:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,넌 벌써\N다음 병 따고 있냐...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,에헤~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,이자카야라고 하면\N제 홈그라운드 아님꽈~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.86,0:13:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,아주 그냥 3배라구요!\N통상의 3배~!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:12.24,Default - A,,0,0,0,,가타카나 위에\N한자도 있고...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:14.64,Default - A,,0,0,0,,뭘까요?\N저도 못 읽겠더라구요
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}처음 와봤지만...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.68,0:13:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}이자카야란 데도\N좀 즐거울지도...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}어른이 돼서\N술 마실 수 있게 되면
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.95,0:13:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}더 즐거워지려나?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,요즘 아내의 옷 취향이\N갑자기 바뀌었더라고...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,스마트폰도\N갑자기 잠금 걸어놓고...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐야?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,아내 핸드폰\N감시까지 하고 살아?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,그런 거 아니라고...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.86,0:13:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,어쩌다\N알아챈 건데...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐, 딱 봐도\N바람난 거네, 그건...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.66,0:13:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,그치...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,하지만 바람 피워도\N당연한 걸지도 모르겠다...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,매일매일\N일만 찾고 살았으니...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.39,0:13:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,아무리 그래도\N그게 왜 당연한 거냐...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,매일 잔업만 계속되고
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.77,0:13:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,쉬는 날에도 접대 골프...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,가끔 일찍 끝나도\N집에 돌아가기 껄끄러워서...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,이렇게\N너랑 마시기나 하니...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.49,0:13:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,난 뭐 하려고\N일하고 있는 걸까...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.16,0:14:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,괜찮냐, 야?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.78,0:14:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,가끔 역 승강장을\N보고 있으면...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,뛰어들고 싶어지는\N내가 있더라니까...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,에이~\N마시고 잊어버려!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,저기요!\N소주 좀 주세요!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.27,0:14:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,예이~!\N소주 한 병 나갑니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}인생이란 어딜 가나\N지옥이란 말인가...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}고등학교 다니는 동안에\N데뷔하지 못했다간
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,800)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}나도 일단\N취직은 해야겠지...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:25.08,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,400)\fna천생연분\fs55\bord4\blur5\c&H332C3E&\3c&H72B8C3&\pos(662.333,450.333)\frx22\fry2\frz6.669}대학에 입학
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:25.08,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,400)\fna천생연분\fs55\bord4\blur5\c&HA6B9CC&\3c&H544B97&\frz30.61\frx24\fry356\pos(945,885)}데뷔에 실패\N\N　취직한다
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.85,0:14:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}대학 갈 수 있을만큼\N머리가 좋은 것도 아니고...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,800)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}내 경우에는 뭐 하러\N가는지도 모를 정도인데~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:33.68,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(270,10)\fna입술l\fs60\bord0\c&H6F6A68&\pos(917.333,281.333)}12월 우무묵 영업 판매 성적
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:33.68,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(270,10)\fna입술l\fs45\bord7\c&H111010&\3c&HF9F8F7&\pos(515,465)}목표 100팩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}에~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}이번달\N우무묵 영업 판매 실적은~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}고토 씨가\N꼴찌였습니다~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.24,0:14:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}또 고토 씨네~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}부장님도\N참 못 됐지~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}고토 씨 그만두게 만들자고\N일부러 영업부로 이동시키고!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:42.94,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna뉴궁서m\fs35\bord5\pos(965,840)\c&H232140&\3c&H898079&}우무묵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}어...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}저..저기...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}우..우무묵\N좀 사주세요...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}숙성도 오래 돼서...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}목넘김도 매끄러운...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\fs90}됐습니다!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:54.87,Default - Right,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1440,10)\fna천생연분\fs55\bord5\blur5\c&H9EA9BF&\3c&H4E499A&\frz337.3\frx28\fry356\pos(1555,415)}영업부로\N\N이전　{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:54.87,Default - Right,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1440,10)\fna천생연분\fs55\bord5\blur5\c&H9EA9BF&\3c&H4E499A&\frx24\fry358\pos(1315,760)\frz338.5}방문판매에\N\N실패　\h{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:54.87,Default - Right,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1440,10)\fna천생연분\fs55\bord5\blur5\c&H9EA9BF&\3c&H4E499A&\frx22\fry0\frz338.2\pos(1265,935)}출근 거부　\N\N방구석 폐인으로
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}손에 잡힐 듯\N알 수 있는!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}막장으로 치닫는\N인생 게임!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,히토리쨩~\N문 좀 열어볼래...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,응?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:15:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,이제 일 같은 거\N안 해도 되니까~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,엄마랑\N또 같이 밥 먹자?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,괜찮지~?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,푸하...
